      • getPreviousDiveSaturation

        private java.lang.String getPreviousDiveSaturation(DiveTable diveTable,
                                                   DiveLog diveLog)
        This function recursively retrieves the previous divelog's saturation while the time since last dive is less than 24 hours. This uses that information to calculate which SaturationGroup the diver should be in after the last dive.
        Parameters:
        diveTable - the dive table to use in the calculation of saturation
        diveLog - the divelog object to get saturation of
        Returns:
        {String} saturationgroup
